title: Ajay
subTitle: Manorama falls in love with Ajay, even though they come from different social backgrounds. They want to get married, but Manorama's uncles try their best to separate the happy couple.

title: Hotel Milan
subTitle: Vipul and Saurabh, two friends, decide to put an end to the misery of couples by starting a love hotel. However, the local political group is not in favour of their venture.

title: Zed Plus
subTitle: Aslam, a villager who runs a small business, accidentally meets the prime minister of India, who grants him special security on his request. Soon, he starts chasing political ambitions.

title: Dharti Kahe Pukar Ke
subTitle: Gangaram brings up his stepbrothers and borrows money to educate them. But, when he fails to repay and faces legal trouble, his brothers strive to help him.

title: Aag
subTitle: A young man seeks a fresh start in a village after enduring tragedy, only to find himself entangled in a conflict that tests his strength and sense of justice.

title: Welcome Wedding
subTitle: A son and his father make a bet that soon spirals out of control, especially after Bollywood celebrity Rakhi Sawant and the media frenzy surrounding her get involved.

title: Anokhi Raat
subTitle: A peculiar mix of people take shelter in a big mansion on a rainy night. So, to pass the time, each begins to narrate their life story.

title: Marudhar Express
subTitle: Marudhar, a naive man who lacks experience in dealing with women, leads his life according to his father's wishes. Hilarity ensues when Marudhar's father forces him to marry the ambitious Chitra.

title: Buddha Mil Gaya
subTitle: Two unsuspecting blokes find themselves entangled in a sinister web of intrigue after harbouring a mysterious millionaire.

title: Deewaar: Let's Bring Our Heroes Home
subTitle: Haunted by the past, Vijay turns to crime, while Ravi, his younger brother, becomes an honest police officer. Fate pits them against each other when Ravi is sent to nab Vijay.

title: Ekkees Tareekh Shubh Muhurat
subTitle: Pandit Girdhari Laal Sharma wants to get his daughter, Radha, married extravagantly but lacks the money for it. He then devises a plan to source the money, unaware of the consequences.

title: Ekkees Tareekh Shubh Muhurat
subTitle: Pandit Girdhari Laal Sharma wants to get his daughter, Radha, married extravagantly but lacks the money for it. He then devises a plan to source the money, unaware of the consequences.

title: Haan Maine Bhi Pyaar Kiya
subTitle: Pooja divorces her husband for being unfaithful and gets a job as secretary to a film star. The two fall in love, before her ex-husband returns and she finds herself confused between the two men.

title: Dariya Dil
subTitle: A wealthy tycoon's clash with a tax officer sparks a sinister plot, as the official's siblings scheme to pilfer the businessman's fortune.

title: Masoom
subTitle: D K Malhotra leads a peaceful life with his wife and two daughters. But all of this changes when he is forced to bring a boy, who is his son from a previous relationship, home after his mother dies.

title: Annadata
subTitle: When Amba Prasad realises the harsh truth that his relatives just care for his money, he leaves home. Upon reaching a village, he meets Arun and Aarti and his life changes forever.

title: Dil
subTitle: A father pretends to be a rich industrialist to improve his son's chances of marrying in to wealth. However, his plan backfires on him when his true identity is found out.

title: Suhaag
subTitle: Twins Amit and Kishan are separated at birth. However, when their paths cross in the future, together they work their way through and strive to overcome challenges.

title: Baaz: A Bird in Danger
subTitle: The police are out on the hunt for a serial killer who targets beautiful women. Their luck changes when a woman who is in love with one of the suspects joins the search.

title: Charitraheen
subTitle: Destiny separates two lovers, Inder and Rama, and Inder marries Kamala. However, events take an unprecedented turn when Inder and Rama cross paths again years later.

title: Kunwara
subTitle: Raju and Urmila fall deeply in love and vow to reunite in India. However, complications arise when Raju agrees to pose as Sharmila's husband before her family.

title: Rafoo Chakkar: Fun on the Run
subTitle: Two brothers, Manjeet and Parmeet, run away from their home in order to avoid getting married. Eventually, they lead a life of crime and things take a turn when they get arrested.

title: Rafoo Chakkar: Fun on the Run
subTitle: Two brothers, Manjeet and Parmeet, run away from their home in order to avoid getting married. Eventually, they lead a life of crime and things take a turn when they get arrested.

title: Kaun Sachcha Kaun Jhootha
subTitle: Karan Saxena, a police officer, arrests Sapna Mathur, a woman accused of killing his fellow constable. Things take a turn when Karan falls in love with her and helps her escape her death sentence.

title: Bewaffa Se Waffa
subTitle: Rukhsar asks her best friend Nagma to marry her husband, Aslam, and mother a child for him when she is unable to do it herself. However, problems begin when Nagma's relatives cause discord among them.

title: Main Tulsi Tere Aangan Ki
subTitle: A wife embraces her husband's illegitimate son as her own in honour of the other woman's memory. However, as time progresses, this starts to seem like a big mistake.

title: Amba
subTitle: When Amba gets her son Rajendra arrested for sexually assaulting their servant's daughter, Rajendra's wife wreaks havoc into their lives as she vows to avenge him.

title: Gone Kesh
subTitle: After being diagnosed with alopecia, a condition that causes rapid hair loss, Enakshi, a young girl, navigates through the trials and tribulations of life.

title: Lorie
subTitle: Geeta is expecting a baby but tragedy strikes and she loses her child. When she finds a little boy, she adopts him as her own but the boy's family accuses her of kidnapping.

title: Jeevan Dhaara
subTitle: Sangeeta, a young woman, decides to sacrifice her dreams and work relentlessly to provide for her family after her father abandons them.

title: Bahurani
subTitle: Amit wants to marry a modern woman but his parents get him married to a village girl, Madhuri. When Amit refuses to accept her as his wife, Madhuri reinvents herself as Malathi and re-enters his life.

title: Kya Kehna
subTitle: A young university student's world is rocked when her brief involvement with a wealthy playboy results in her pregnancy.

title: Beta
subTitle: After the death of his mother, Raju's father re-marries, but his stepmother is only after the family's money. When Raju eventually marries, his wife tries to make him realise what kind of woman his stepmother is.
